        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="基于Hexo的个人网站制作简明教程"><a href="#基于Hexo的个人网站制作简明教程" class="headerlink" title="基于Hexo的个人网站制作简明教程"></a>基于Hexo的个人网站制作简明教程</h2><p>文末有我参考的教程，那个比较详细，遇到问题可以咨询我。</p><p>我的机器：<code>ubuntu 22.04 / nodejs14</code></p><h3 id="1、hexo配置"><a href="#1、hexo配置" class="headerlink" title="1、hexo配置"></a>1、hexo配置</h3><p>网站：<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">Hexo</a>  通过访问这个网站我们可以看到如何使用</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line">hexo init blog</span><br><span class="line">cd blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>上面是基础的一键部署，注意：前提是已安装nodejs和git</p><h3 id="2、主题选择"><a href="#2、主题选择" class="headerlink" title="2、主题选择"></a>2、主题选择</h3><p>如果不喜欢<code>hexo</code>默认的主题，可以选择一个主题进行配置，如图所示</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucky-lcy-best/img-repo/uploadImg/fix-dir/img/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/2023/01/14/14-50-57-54e5bfb954694190f6ff627146288874-image-20230114144200657-27851f.png" class="lazyload placeholder" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucky-lcy-best/img-repo/uploadImg/fix-dir/img/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/2023/01/14/14-50-57-54e5bfb954694190f6ff627146288874-image-20230114144200657-27851f.png" srcset="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp" alt="image-20230114144200657" style="zoom:50%;" /><h3 id="3、个人配置"><a href="#3、个人配置" class="headerlink" title="3、个人配置"></a>3、个人配置</h3><p>对于原始的主题配置自己的信息</p><p>主要在你主题下面的<code>_config.yml</code>文件以及<code>blog</code>根目录下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件</p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucky-lcy-best/img-repo/uploadImg/fix-dir/img/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/2023/01/14/14-50-57-7f68c64b5344b41fdcd214118dd935dc-image-20230114144553704-cf6791.png" class="lazyload placeholder" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucky-lcy-best/img-repo/uploadImg/fix-dir/img/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/2023/01/14/14-50-57-7f68c64b5344b41fdcd214118dd935dc-image-20230114144553704-cf6791.png" srcset="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp" alt="image-20230114144553704" style="zoom:50%;" /><h3 id="4、注意"><a href="#4、注意" class="headerlink" title="4、注意"></a>4、注意</h3><p>在你的github下面创建一个仓库，命名建议<code>用户名.github.io</code>，比如我的是<code>lucky-lcy-best.github.io</code></p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucky-lcy-best/img-repo/uploadImg/fix-dir/img/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/2023/01/14/14-50-57-76d27d4708d3e559d8ffb4d82eec0114-image-20230114144743877-6b4861.png" class="lazyload placeholder" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lucky-lcy-best/img-repo/uploadImg/fix-dir/img/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95/2023/01/14/14-50-57-76d27d4708d3e559d8ffb4d82eec0114-image-20230114144743877-6b4861.png" srcset="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-cd38920285d125be80b3eb504052c550_b.webp" alt="image-20230114144553704" style="zoom:50%;" /><h3 id="5、部署方式"><a href="#5、部署方式" class="headerlink" title="5、部署方式"></a>5、部署方式</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean #清除之前的东西</span><br><span class="line">hexo g # 生成静态资源</span><br><span class="line">hexo d # 部署到github</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我参考的教程：<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44763569/article/details/106435118">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44763569/article/details/106435118</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
